title: R-Undelete 5.0 Build 164588 (Install + Portable)
description:
R-Undelete 5.0 Build 164588 (Install + Portable)

About this release

Release date: 06/06/2016
Install: Run setup, copy cracked files to installation directory and overwrite existing ones, use keygen to generate serial
Portable: Both versions are patched / registered, simply unzip archive and run your version

About R-Undelete

It's easy-to-use yet powerful undelete solution for Windows OS users. In comparison with the free Home version R-UNDELETE recovers lost files from NTFS, NTFS5 (created or updated by Win2000/XP/2003/Vista/2008/Win7/Win8/Win10) disks as well as recovers them from FAT (FAT12, FAT16, FAT32, exFAT) disks

Using the same unique data recovery technology IntelligentScan as the heavyweight R-Studio, R-Undelete is an inexpensive and easy-to-use yet powerful file undelete solution for FAT and NTFS file systems.
R-Undelete recovers files on any local disks recognized by the software.
In addition, raw file recovery (scan for known file types) can be used for heavily damaged or unknown file systems.
For user's convenience R-Undelete can be run from disks and folders context menu. Graphic files, video and audio files (all files are supported if a proper codec is installed on the system) can be previewed before they are recovered. 

Homepage http://www.r-undelete.com/
